 data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FZOqrQnxq0jA&d=GlETU%2Fuc5qoZzc1QHf9C2tAAr5%2FwdiPol2qeWm%2BM8v8%3D&h=bc5e2ed8\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ZOqrQnxq0jA</a><br />\n<br />\n請記住「團結」係雙刃劍<br />\n所以一定要三思而行<br />\n<br />\nBe water, be considerate, be safe."},{"pid":"d68dc2f1ded1be73aeb6f2f05b87e99bc37b48d6","tid":1464053,"uid":177678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:28:12.000Z","msg":"希望各位仲記得2014年點解輸<br />\n仲要輸得咁徹底<br />\nWe will be back<br />\n我地2019 back左啦<br />\n但運動而家同2014年運動個結尾係一樣<br />\n下次back唔知又係幾時"},{"pid":"730442aab0e7f7fcfbb620ddd120932a97804f80","tid":1464053,"uid":33736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5dc62d8d6b3ff8f7be7109573211b55f129f559c","tid":1464053,"uid":165925,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:26:53.000Z","msg":"「我地而家係要同香港政府攬炒」<br />\n試詳說明之<br />\n<br />\n「唔需要再講咩民意」<br />\n咁即係成個香港係得你一個有份？<br />\n<br />\n「我地一早已經比人認定左係暴徒做乜都錯」<br />\n失敗論？<br />\n<br />\n「只要香港玩完 我地先有將來」<br />\n你啲因果關係係點黎？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[另外順便講一講<br />\n［size=5]<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />[/size=5]<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">請</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><br />\n部分黑警察停止濫用武力<br />\n部分示威者停止暴力衝擊<br />\n政府作出讓步並不再企硬<br />\n歡迎和理非繼續<span style=\"color: pink;\">合法</span>示威</span></span><br />\n<br />\n齊上齊落同時請考慮每個行動既利與弊<br />\n否則恐怕變成文革2.0<br />\n目標稍有雜質 <br />\n大家就骨牌效應集體做偏左<br />\n花你搭車痾屎時間去重溫<br />\n鏗鏘集：文革五十年（上）<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ZOqrQnxq0jA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FZOqrQnxq0jA&d=GlETU%2Fuc5qoZzc1QHf9C2tAAr5%2FwdiPol2qeWm%2BM8v8%3D&h=bc5e2ed8\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ZOqrQnxq0jA</a><br />\n<br />\n請記住「團結」係雙刃劍<br />\n所以一定要三思而行<br />\n<br />\nBe water, be considerate, be safe."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T14:29:38.000Z","msg":"文革2.0你都講得出<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hah